  <reg:title>Time Period for Review Regulation</reg:title>
  <reg:amsincluded>[Last amended March 22, 2021 by B.C. Reg. 89/2021]</reg:amsincluded>
  <reg:regpitid>164_2015_pit</reg:regpitid>
  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section toc="false" id="d1e28">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Definition</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>In this regulation, <in:term>Act</in:term> means the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/19001_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Workers Compensation Act</in:doc></bcl:link>.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d1e47">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Prescribed time period</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>For the purposes of section 270 (1) (b) <in:desc>[shorter time period for requesting review]</in:desc> of the Act, the time period to file a request for a review of any of the following is 45 days:</bcl:text>
      <bcl:paragraph id="d1e58">
        <bcl:num>a</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>a Board decision or order referred to in section 268 (1) (a) <in:desc>[decision or order respecting an occupational health or safety matter]</in:desc> of the Act; </bcl:text>
      </bcl:paragraph>
      <bcl:paragraph id="d1e67">
        <bcl:num>b</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>a Board decision referred to in section 268 (1) (c) (iii) (A) <in:desc>[decision respecting levy of contribution from specific employer]</in:desc> of the Act.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:paragraph>
      <bcl:hnote>[en. B.C. Reg. 89/2021, Sch. 1, s. 5.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions relevant to the enactment of this regulation: <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/19001_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Workers Compensation Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, R.S.B.C. 2019, c. 1, s. 109 (3).]</reg:provisionsnote>
  </reg:content>
